text: Stetten am kalten Markt is a municipality in Sigmaringen in Baden-Württemberg in Germany. The towns of Nusplingen, Frohnstetten, Storzingen and Glashütte are part of Stetten am kalten Markt. The current mayor of Stetten am kalten Markt is Maik Lehn from the CDU since 2015. == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Sigmaringen (district)
